  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零售POS系统的异步处理流程。核心是从聚合根产生事件，经过事件存储，最终触发副作用。我想把Event Store作为中央枢纽，然后有一个Reactor组件负责把事件转换成队列任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以Reactor是监听Event Store的变化，然后往Queue里推送任务？那Queue Worker是独立拉取还是被动接收？另外副作用执行失败的话需要重试机制吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Reactor主动Push Job到Queue，Queue Worker是消费端。重试是必须的——我们画一个alt分支：成功时Worker标记任务完成，失败时走Retry逻辑。Side Effect要单独作为一个参与者，比如发邮件或调支付网关。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Retry Job",
        "Mark Job as Completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主链路画出来：Aggregate往Event Store存事件，Event Store通知Reactor，Reactor推任务进Queue，Queue Worker取出处理，最后Worker调用Side Effect执行。六个参与者都就位了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Event Store到Reactor的箭头方向确认一下——是Dispatch Event，表示事件已存储后主动分发。还有Worker和Side Effect之间是双向的，Side Effect执行完要把结果返回给Worker，这样Worker才能决定走成功分支还是失败分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整了，E到R是Dispatch Event，W和S之间加了双向箭头：W调用S执行，S返回Success或Failure。然后我在alt里拆了两条回线——成功时W通知Q标记完成，失败时W通知Q重试。这样符合你的设计吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dispatch Event",
        "Execute Side Effect",
        "Return Success",
        "Return Failure",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "有个细节：Queue Worker到Queue的两条消息方向反了。应该是Worker告诉Queue去标记完成或重试，不是Queue主动推给Worker。你现在的箭头好像画成Q指向W了，需要调过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修复！现在W-Q的箭头方向正确了：Worker主动上报状态，Queue被动接收标记。整个流程闭环了——从聚合产生事件，到最终副作用执行，成功失败都有处理路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Mark Job as Completed",
        "Retry Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
